---
import { Star, RefreshCw, ArrowLeftRight, ChartBar, Smartphone, Shield } from '@lucide/astro';
---

<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">

  <div style="background: var(--color-bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: var(--spacing-xl);">
    <div style="color: var(--color-accent); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);">
      <Star size={24} aria-hidden="true" />
    </div>
    <h3 style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm); color: var(--color-text);">
      Expanding Wild
    </h3>
    <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
      The Starburst Wild lands on reels 2, 3, or 4 and expands to fill the entire reel — triggering a free re-spin.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="background: var(--color-bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: var(--spacing-xl);">
    <div style="color: var(--color-accent); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);">
      <RefreshCw size={24} aria-hidden="true" />
    </div>
    <h3 style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm); color: var(--color-text);">
      Re-Spins (up to 3×)
    </h3>
    <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
      Each Wild expansion locks the reel and triggers a re-spin. A chain of three re-spins with locked Wilds is the biggest moment the game offers.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="background: var(--color-bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: var(--spacing-xl);">
    <div style="color: var(--color-accent); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);">
      <ArrowLeftRight size={24} aria-hidden="true" />
    </div>
    <h3 style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm); color: var(--color-text);">
      Win Both Ways
    </h3>
    <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
      All 10 paylines evaluate symbols left-to-right and right-to-left — effectively 20 win opportunities per spin.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="background: var(--color-bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: var(--spacing-xl);">
    <div style="color: var(--color-accent); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);">
      <ChartBar size={24} aria-hidden="true" />
    </div>
    <h3 style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm); color: var(--color-text);">
      Low Volatility
    </h3>
    <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
      Hit frequency of 22.6% means roughly one win in every five spins. Your bankroll lasts longer than on high-variance titles.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="background: var(--color-bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: var(--spacing-xl);">
    <div style="color: var(--color-accent); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);">
      <Smartphone size={24} aria-hidden="true" />
    </div>
    <h3 style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm); color: var(--color-text);">
      Mobile Optimised
    </h3>
    <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
      HTML5 build runs in any mobile browser on Android or iOS. No app download. No installation. Full game on any screen.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="background: var(--color-bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: var(--spacing-xl);">
    <div style="color: var(--color-accent); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);">
      <Shield size={24} aria-hidden="true" />
    </div>
    <h3 style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm); color: var(--color-text);">
      Certified Fair
    </h3>
    <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
      NetEnt's RNG is audited by eCOGRA and iTech Labs. RTP 96.09% verified across billions of spins.
    </p>
  </div>

</div>
